話日本人覺得三文魚唔係貴(正)野<br />\n<br />\n好似香港人有人鐘意食紅衫魚<br />\n唔=紅衫魚有東星班地位</blockquote><br />\n乜香港人覺得三文魚係貴野咩？"},{"pid":"181a32691954ff2d6d7fdf853d03f2ddf8f97c4b","tid":411893,"uid":35882,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"老一輩唔食啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />後生個啲多數都食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cce79d87929cbb1ac32d6bb1a1752a04b6721e0","tid":411893,"uid":49359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係話日本人覺得三文魚唔係貴(正)野<br />\n<br />\n好似香港人有人鐘意食紅衫魚<br />\n唔=紅衫魚有東星班地位</blockquote><br />\n紅衫魚以前就平<br />\n有時石班仲平過佢"},{"pid":"2285ee2753ec802e383899f62ce31851ad22ae02","tid":411893,"uid":140802,"like":24,"dislike":9,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該係話日本人覺得三文魚唔係貴(正)野<br />\n<br />\n好似香港人有人鐘意食紅衫魚<br />\n唔=紅衫魚有東星班地位</blockquote><br />\n乜香港人覺得三文魚係貴野咩？</blockquote><br />\n見親D C9同港女次次去放題叫幾十件三文魚<br />\n去BUFFET就話:有三文魚呀快D去搶啦 幫我排啦<br />\n我小學雞時代去劣食明將 都見到D C9同港女搶 三文魚壽司 淨係食三文魚 D飯就搵紙巾同碟姐住佢<br />\n我就笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n覺唔覺三文魚係貴野就因人而異啦<br />\n不過香港人除左三文魚<br />\n仲分得出其他Sashimi係咩魚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3e1106ae4f064b90325a4f9569f3db3f2a22a0","tid":411893,"uid":48222,"like":38,"dislike":13,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/155708_7c062364e17eca6388b8fc80ea9ae98f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F155708_7c062364e17eca6388b8fc80ea9ae98f.jpg&h=00c29fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個肥婆咁似emilia<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64b5c43c53d74