,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:12:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前鍾意食生三文魚，但依加發現火炙三文魚仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生既不了<br />\n燒既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a000aeb63c2b3bdb6deb0ae489e3372cd74bb4","tid":411893,"uid":26161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>曼德拉效應</blockquote><br />\n就係你d on9仔成日乜鳩都曼德拉效應</blockquote><br />\n真心出現了</blockquote><br />\n真你老母心 假膠同弱智你識唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc4a5fef70f16fd1ba279c267bd77142e7748cb","tid":411893,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"菜潺果然食開高級嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdfcf101e41f15f6c73a9767592bc372ffa5d60","tid":411893,"uid":41765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:47:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蔡san</blockquote><br />\n係得佢話"},{"pid":"5439429a4290bf449420bc24b7dc33afe1e9707c","tid":411893,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該係話日本人覺得三文魚唔係貴(正)野<br />\n<br />\n好似香港人有人鐘意食紅衫魚<br />\n唔=紅衫魚有東星班地位</blockquote><br />\n紅衫魚以前就平<br />\n有時石班仲平過佢</blockquote><br />\n真說話"},{"pid":"a2613c5e9036cad10dfa7db64190c8de9f41b34b","tid":411893,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/155708_7c062364e17eca6388b8fc80ea9ae98f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F155708_7c062364e17eca6388b8fc80ea9ae98f.jpg&h=00c29fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個肥婆咁似emilia<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打重口味"},{"pid":"ebd977084e07de65c6961ce6f61848a84a6c8786","tid":411893,"uid":149791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:53:42.000Z","msg":"係你on9姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e7813ecfe64c1d776fa6c6b4fc25db085541b3","tid":411893,"uid":34810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:56:39.000Z","msg":"日本啲三文魚唔知點解唔好食<br />\n啲色水又怪"},{"pid":"a093ebaa1c39af14bef0a3d9835d28cdafbecd8b","tid":411893,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"要不是蔡欄，日本人都唔識食三文魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f265fc60c444c633b7ab68bc75d0b34ab6606ae8","tid":411893,"uid":63870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:02:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食三文魚魚生係挪威開始<br />\n之後傳到香港<br />\n日本係再之後先興<br />\n<br />\n崇日撚以為全世界得日本人食魚生.....</blockquote><br />\n關崇唔崇咩野事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條友自己先係崇日撚，認為食魚生=高級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f614cf17b5df74589a5f68b3055b5a064e30da","tid":411893,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:04:13.000Z","msg":"係魚市場都見佢地買黎食，不過唔識揀囉，專揀D垃圾位黎食"},{"pid":"e3269d2e5d29f21e4bbfb21a0e2ae03f5a6e2982","tid":411893,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"日本咁多人<br />\n個個人唔食咩"},{"pid":"0e45b84e34acf3dc215bd2eda30c1576034989a1","tid":411893,"uid":134383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:29:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本人食唔食我唔知 不過我自己唔食</blockquote><br />\n無人想知你食唔食，ok？"},{"pid":"8499d2e239fd180eab472959cb3100e2ab0f1e88","tid":411893,"uid":17003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:3